{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/lemp-stack-on-centos-7-red-hat","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>A very quick how-to guide on installing NGINX, MySQL and PHP, otherwise known as a LEMP stack on CentOS 7 (and usable on Red Hat 7 as well). <em>Image from Digital Ocean <a href=\"https://twitter.com/digitalocean/status/496697898248065025\">link</a>.</em></p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h2 id=\"1-install-mysql-mariadb\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-install-mysql-mariadb\" aria-label=\"1 install mysql mariadb permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Install MySQL (mariadb)</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell-session\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell-session line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell-session\"><span class=\"token output\">yum install mariadb mariadb-server\nmariadb restart\nsudo /usr/bin/mysql_secure_installation</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"2-add-the-nginx-repository\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-add-the-nginx-repository\" aria-label=\"2 add the nginx repository permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Add the NGINX repository</h2>\n<p>Create the file named /etc/yum.repos.d/nginx.repo with the following contents:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ini\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-ini line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"token header\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token section-name selector\">nginx</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">nginx repo</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">baseurl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">http://nginx.org/packages/mainline/centos/7/$basearch/</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">gpgcheck</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">enabled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">1</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"3-install-nginx\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-install-nginx\" aria-label=\"3 install nginx permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Install NGINX</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell-session\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell-session line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell-session\"><span class=\"token output\">yum install nginx\nservice nginx start\nservice nginx status</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"4-allow-nginx-through-the-firewall\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-allow-nginx-through-the-firewall\" aria-label=\"4 allow nginx through the firewall permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Allow NGINX through the firewall</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell-session\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell-session line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell-session\"><span class=\"token output\">firewall-cmd --set-default-zone=home\nfirewall-cmd --permanent --zone=home --add-service=http\nfirewall-cmd --reload</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"5-install-php\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-install-php\" aria-label=\"5 install php permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Install PHP</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell-session\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell-session line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell-session\"><span class=\"token output\">sudo yum install php-fpm php-mysql</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"6-autostart-mysql-nginx-and-php-on-boot\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-autostart-mysql-nginx-and-php-on-boot\" aria-label=\"6 autostart mysql nginx and php on boot permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. Autostart MySQL, NGINX and PHP on boot</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell-session\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell-session line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell-session\"><span class=\"token output\">sudo chkconfig --levels 235 mariadb on sudo chkconfig --levels 235 nginx on sudo chkconfig --levels 235 php-fpm on</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>And we are finished! Start configuring your new LEMP stack on CentOS</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 850px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ea8356af59bd705c714f1c4cb92b6cfa/5f7f3/successsss.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.08920187793427%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"nginx-success\"\n        title=\"nginx-success\"\n        src=\"/static/ea8356af59bd705c714f1c4cb92b6cfa/d6170/successsss.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ea8356af59bd705c714f1c4cb92b6cfa/53f68/successsss.png 213w,\n/static/ea8356af59bd705c714f1c4cb92b6cfa/df70d/successsss.png 425w,\n/static/ea8356af59bd705c714f1c4cb92b6cfa/d6170/successsss.png 850w,\n/static/ea8356af59bd705c714f1c4cb92b6cfa/5f7f3/successsss.png 971w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"A very quick how-to guide on installing NGINX, MySQL and PHP, otherwise known as a LEMP stack on CentOS 7 (and usable on Red Hat 7 as well…","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/calvin.me/calvin.me/master/posts/2014-08-27-lemp-stack-on-centos-7-red-hat/index.md","frontmatter":{"title":"Install LEMP Stack on CentOS 7 (Red Hat 7)","categories":["Web"],"tags":["centos","lemp","mysql","nginx","php"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b95906031d448fc56ddd7cc65edad117/ccc8a/thumbnail.png","srcSet":"/static/b95906031d448fc56ddd7cc65edad117/ccc8a/thumbnail.png 150w,\n/static/b95906031d448fc56ddd7cc65edad117/67d4a/thumbnail.png 300w","sizes":"150px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/b95906031d448fc56ddd7cc65edad117/3554d/thumbnail.webp 150w,\n/static/b95906031d448fc56ddd7cc65edad117/c437f/thumbnail.webp 300w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"150px"}]},"width":150,"height":150}}}}}},"pageContext":{"filter":"/^.*\\/\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}-lemp-stack-on-centos-7-red-hat\\/.*$/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}